==Koan-appearances==
Xuefeng occurs in several koans:
* [[The Gateless Gate|The Mumonkan]]: koan 13;
* [[Blue Cliff Record]]: koan 5, 22, 49, 51, 66;
* [[Kōan#The Book of Equanimity|The Book of Equanimity]]: koan 24, 33, 50, 55.

